4.02	David_Reekie	David Reekie	David Reekie is an eminent English Glass Sculptor who uses drawing and glass casting to express his unique vision of the human condition. His art can be found in the Victoria and Albert Museum in London and the Carnegie Museum of Art in Pittsburgh, as well as in several other public collections in the United Kingdom.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/25/David_Reekie_in_studio_2007%2C_photographyer_Duncan_Reekie_72dpi.jpg/250px-David_Reekie_in_studio_2007%2C_photographyer_Duncan_Reekie_72dpi.jpg
